Commit Message: FFS .. GitHub renamed the MASTER branch to main ... stupid GitHub

v0.1.0-alpha.2

So we have the correct image link on Pypi as well ...
[CSS] margin on last endpoint element fixed
show a warning when status couldn't be loaded

Release 1.0.0

Since there is not much to test after all, let's just go with 1.0.0 right from the start
[FIX] Local variable might be referenced before being initialized
useragent moved to constants instead of __init__
Checked for compatibility with Python 3.9 and Django 3.2
Error handling on connection error to ESI status

Minimum requirements updated

  - Python 3.7
  - Alliance Auth v2.9.3
AA>=2.9.4 is testing for Python 3.11 and so do we
We don't serve any external JS or CSS, so this is not needed
Added check for merge conflicts to pre-commit config
[FIX] We should include the right app

[FIX] Category with names containing a space couldn't be opened

e.g. Faction Warfare
Updated tox tests for the new alpha version of Alliance Auth 3
[CHANGE] Internal changes/improvements and min. AA version raised
[MISC] Test suite updated - Python 3.11 tests no longer allowed to fail
